We've added additional org performance metrics for connection pools, Visualforce, and sync/async callout errors. You can also view recommendations to improve SOQL performance in the database CPU investigation. And you can export ApexGuru insights in PDF format.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Unlimited Edition. Scale Center isnâ€™t supported in Government Cloud Plus.

Scale Center is generally available at no additional cost for all Unlimited Edition Full Copy Sandbox, Signature, and Scale Test customers. You can enable Scale Center for five Standard (non-SysAdmin) users per org.

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Scale, and then click Scale Center.
title: Deploy Scalable Apps with Salesforce Scale Center
